{"tid":1242211,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"CLS 麥當勞你個採購同我入一入黎！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T15:22:46.000Z","uid":82530,"like":50,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"757fabf0caf2cc268663072c2498281e429bb28e","tid":1242211,"uid":82530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"買左個早餐外賣 企埋一邊等<br />\n見到個阿嬋嬲嬲地走埋去<br />\n話行出去兩步個袋就斷左 <br />\n叫人幫佢換個第杯 仲話一定要加多個袋俾佢<br />\n我心諗。  肯定係自己唔小心跌左落地下扮哂野<br />\n依家d客咁麻煩<br />\n<br />\n點知 到我拎到個外賣 行出間m記<br />\n我比個阿嬋勁少少。 行左有十步咁多<br />\n個外賣袋成個柄位就斷開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好嬲好嬲好嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個採購有冇用腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街連鎖餐廳你要削減成本<br />\n都唔係要換個一杯野飲都負重唔到既廢袋<br />\n唔好同我講環保 環保撚同我死開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環保環保你呀爸呀媽咁環保你都出唔到世<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/19/112807_80cfe40db6bc97fd0e4acce9974bdf7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F19%2F112807_80cfe40db6bc97fd0e4acce9974bdf7e.png&h=07bba59e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a1525d42e20a1881fd21beecdf767ebc88819eb","tid":1242211,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb672c84a50febac256f818dbe1135cb6e02f6a","tid":1242211,"uid":227414,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:33:18.000Z","msg":"d袋越黎越薄"},{"pid":"140ddf1e59da8edddca3f9843fe47b5fe912d98d","tid":1242211,"uid":174601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淘寶野咁上下"},{"pid":"e29a0ffecc92da8bb0530926d244407e7806cbd0","tid":1242211,"uid":77092,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:37:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd2a6fc0319a2bdc52b8ff83c83223e36479f855","tid":1242211,"uid":257422,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c384bc7476bef2434493b7e9d5434eb4db1b248","tid":1242211,"uid":28831,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"仲食m記<br />\n所以話香港邊有可能有民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64424fa906d5b4b61ad787fe71ffb5ef4a090723","tid":1242211,"uid":43114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:40:45.000Z","msg":"係店內行廿步先走嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a936c1349a9234f7e0437638560c565b052e529","tid":1242211,"uid":73527,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"我都試過次買扭扭粉外賣<br />\n行到屋企樓下 成個袋下面穿撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌佢老母嬲撚到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe4cb172dedf469b187f1dd97b695ddc5af6c63","tid":1242211,"uid":106307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"有時窮到燶食個m記都嬲到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330304db1990fd68e620e893507f2024fa3ec659","tid":1242211,"uid":107297,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T17:01:52.000Z","msg":"哇屌好撚驚麥麥送D人會跌左杯野照比人"},{"pid":"34db2f9991b935875541131fc8614a1f2ba0539a","tid":1242211,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T20:29:07.000Z","msg":"時間教得啱啱好 夠出到門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced00137c4b88a636c1307cf38af849a96e82131","tid":1242211,"uid":47658,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5c384bc7476bef2434493b7